      "7": "It|strong=\"H7200\"will|strong=\"H4310\"happen|strong=\"H1961\"that|strong=\"H7200\"all|strong=\"H3605\"those|strong=\"H3605\"who|strong=\"H4310\"look|strong=\"H7200\"at|strong=\"H7200\"you|strong=\"H3605\"will|strong=\"H4310\"flee|strong=\"H5074\"from|strong=\"H4480\"you|strong=\"H3605\", and|strong=\"H7200\"say, ‘Nineveh|strong=\"H5210\"is|strong=\"H4310\"laid waste|strong=\"H7703\"! Who|strong=\"H4310\"will|strong=\"H4310\"mourn|strong=\"H5110\"for|strong=\"H1245\"her|strong=\"H3605\"?’ Where|strong=\"H4480\"will|strong=\"H4310\"I|strong=\"H7200\"seek|strong=\"H1245\"comforters|strong=\"H5162\"for|strong=\"H1245\"you|strong=\"H3605\"?”",
