      "19": "There|strong=\"H3605\"is|strong=\"H4310\"no|strong=\"H3808\"healing|strong=\"H3545\"your|strong=\"H3605\"wound|strong=\"H4347\", for|strong=\"H3588\"your|strong=\"H3605\"injury|strong=\"H7667\"is|strong=\"H4310\"fatal. All|strong=\"H3605\"who|strong=\"H4310\"hear|strong=\"H8085\"the|strong=\"H3605\"report|strong=\"H8088\"of|strong=\"H3709\"you|strong=\"H3588\"clap|strong=\"H8628\"their|strong=\"H3605\"hands|strong=\"H3709\"over|strong=\"H5921\"you|strong=\"H3588\", for|strong=\"H3588\"who|strong=\"H4310\"hasn’t felt your|strong=\"H3605\"endless cruelty|strong=\"H7451\"?"
